How to setup Terraform on Windows

1. Download Windows exe file
2. unzip and copy the file to any directory if wants to change
3. Add to variable
     - Open System properties
    - Advanced
    - Environment variables
    - in System variables, Select  "path", Edit it, 
        click New and Paste the path of directory contains "terraform.exe"
    - VS code change from Powershell to git-bash
 
- May need to change git-bash in VS code if needs to follow the commands